Usage: blog [--version] [--help] <command> [args]

Commands:
  add [post|draft]		Create a new post or draft.
  edit <id>			Edit post <id>.
  ls [id]			List posts, or post [id].
  rm <id>			Delete post <id>.
  update			Update blog.
  push				Publish blog.
  clean				Clean out blog cache.
  regen				Alias of blog clean && blog update.
  help <command>		Display help for <command>.

Options:
  --version			Display the current version.
  --help			Display help.

See 'blog help <command>' for more information on a specific command.
